I made this recipe with a few modifications and got rave reviews from family & friends who all claim to be Carrot Cake lovers. My modifications: 1 c white sugar & 1/2 c brown sugar 1 c veg oil 1/2 rounded c drained crushed pineapple 1 3/4 tsp cinnamon 1 tsp nutmeg 1 tsp ground cloves 1/2 c raisins soaked in dark rum (drain off rum before using) Be careful to not over bake.

