Question and then helpful pointer. Has anyone used this recipe for cupcakes? What timing adjustment should be made for baking? Some tweaking that makes this cake PERFECT: -frosting should have 2 cups of sugar not 4 - Grate the carrots in the food processor with grating attachment and then reinsert mixture (in batches) in food processor with pulsing blade till carrot resembles very fine corn meal. This makes the cake moist, dense but airy and absolutely delicious.

