Rating: 3
Great cake recipe! I will definitely make it again. I have one comment on the frosting though. For those of you whose frosting came out runny, or have problems with lumps, do the following: instead on throwing all the frosting ingredients in one bowl and mixing you should first blend the cream cheese and butter toghether until smooth and creamy. Then add the little powder sugar.

